title: Bonus Sesh Preview - Leah McSweeney
description: Enjoy this special sneak peek of a Bonus Bitch Sesh from Stitcher Premium. Casey and Danielle sit down with Leah McSweeney (RHONY) to talk about her new book, Ramona's floor poop, and the reunion that never was.
